MIT License

prd-spec-generator — a stateless reducer that turns a feature description
into a production-ready PRD with multi-judge verification, deterministic
Hard Output Rules validation, and research-evidence-backed strategy
selection. Part of the ai-architect ecosystem
(https://github.com/cdeust/Cortex,
 https://github.com/cdeust/automatised-pipeline,
 https://github.com/cdeust/zetetic-team-subagents).

